#!   CATEGORY="&quot;FGP Tools&quot;"
#!   DESCRIPTION="&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Description&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#10;&lt;p&gt;This custom transformer extracts from the flatten XML (XHTML), the tags of the metadata information and transformed them into FME attributes. The XHTML tags information are renamed with the appropriate name to facilitate the following processes.  The custom transformer deletes the flatten XML attributes.&lt;/p&gt;&#10;&lt;p&gt;Note: This custom transformer will not produce the same result if the HTML tags are modified by the owner of the web site even for a small change in the layout of the information.  Some XHTML tags are not optional so it&apos;s impossible to distinguish a missing tag from a tag that was renamed.&lt;/p&gt;&#10;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Input Ports&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#10;&lt;ul&gt;&#10;&lt;li&gt;The flatten XHTML code.  On feature per dataset.&lt;/li&gt;&#10;&lt;/ul&gt;&#10;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Output Ports&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#10;&lt;ul&gt;&#10;&lt;li&gt;The fatures with extracted information in FME attributes.&lt;/li&gt;&#10;&lt;/ul&gt;"
